{"tid":920161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU連掃3獎 撼贏潤娥奪人氣獎惹爭議","createTime":"2018-11-28T15:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T08:52:59.000Z","uid":34643,"like":63,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"357866483b1a23c3c90dc7c497601cb038520beb","tid":920161,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181128/_2018112821285795261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181128%2F_2018112821285795261.jpg&h=09922884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU(右)撼贏潤娥奪人氣獎。<br />\n<br />\n由STARNEWS主辦的「2018 Asia Artist Awards」（AAA）在仁川舉行，日前AAA公布由網友投選的人氣獎惹爭議，潤娥失落人氣女演員獎給IU，但潤娥仍悉心打扮亮相。<br />\n第3屆「2018 Asia Artist Awards」星光熠熠，出現於紅地氈的包括秀智、潤娥、IU、宣美、李秉憲、李昇基、丁海寅等，今屆典禮由李聖經和Super Junior隊長利特主持，頒獎禮前大會已宣布由網友投選的人氣歌手和男女演員獎，歌手IU憑《我的大叔》擊敗少女時代成員潤娥奪<span style=\"color: red;\">人氣女演員</span>，有網友投訴大會曾兩度作出刪票行動，導致投給潤娥的票被取消，最後更敗給IU。<br />\n潤娥似乎未有理會傳聞，悉心打扮出席頒獎禮，更與IU一黑一白雙映成趣。潤娥最後空手而回，相反IU亦獲得<span style=\"color: red;\">亞洲最火紅演員獎</span>和<span style=\"color: red;\">年度藝人</span>。IU在獲頒人氣女演員獎後表示︰「因為是粉絲票選的獎，我一定會放在房間。」最火紅歌手則由男團Wanna One捧走。<br />\n紅到美國的男團防彈少年團（BTS）獲4獎成大贏家，包括日前公布的人氣歌手外，亦年度藝人、獲得韓國觀光公社的感謝狀和與女團TWICE成Fabulous歌手獎得主。<br />\n李秉憲都獲韓國觀光公社的感謝狀（演員部門）、年度藝人，以及與河正宇共分Fabulous演員獎，李秉憲和河正宇兩位型男同台，台下觀眾相當興奮，河正宇首度出席AAA，他表示感到好開心，又提到明年跟李秉憲一齊拍攝新電影。<br />\n年度藝人方面，演員部門得獎者有主持李聖經、俊昊、丁海寅、柳俊烈、IU、李昇基、朱智勳、柳延錫、李秉憲和河正宇。歌手部門則有Wanna One、iKON、TWICE、GOT7、宣美、BTS、Zico、MONSTA X、MAMAMOO和NU'EST W得獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181128/_2018112821285856079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181128%2F_2018112821285856079.jpg&h=726109fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181128/_2018112821285866174.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181128%2F_2018112821285866174.jpg&h=7138a5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潤娥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181128/_2018112821285710654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181128%2F_2018112821285710654.jpg&h=064f60e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秀智。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181128/_2018112821285917738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181128%2F_2018112821285917738.jpg&h=1ee57e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU連奪3獎。"},{"pid":"f0c738a407e4d02a10dfc2a1fead7d824bdd0fdc","tid":920161,"uid":34643,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:31:43.000Z","msg":"低b妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/6f91b5b60dfe82a233b8d935b95237d4/5C01366B/t51.12442-15/e35/44830269_502490316931695_672649625568497371_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F6f91b5b60dfe82a233b8d935b95237d4%2F5C01366B%2Ft51.12442-15%2Fe35%2F44830269_502490316931695_672649625568497371_n.jpg&h=37ce44de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/6cb8d83410946dbbe11448643865365e/5C00D978/t51.12442-15/e35/45347871_535308063609145_6981318087330372447_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F6cb8d83410946dbbe11448643865365e%2F5C00D978%2Ft51.12442-15%2Fe35%2F45347871_535308063609145_6981318087330372447_n.jpg&h=3b0fddcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"987d2befe409a5acba7fc3c44d4c4ed2a5cbe1ec","tid":920161,"uid":34643,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ww4.s